parameters: Ahem... Uh, I wanted to say, uh... Thank you, Mom.
For everything you’ve done for me recently.
\N[1]... I had fun too, and I’ve loved our time together...
BUT... I don’t know, maybe this is for the best.
The meds will help you sleep soundly, you’ll finally have
the apartment to yourself, and it will be good for your
Even if, I mean... You’ll still come over to visit, right?
We could still... Do things, even if...
I can’t promise you that, Baby. I wish I could.
It’s getting harder to hide our... Activities...
And if anyone were to find out...
Even if, we’d still have each other. Isn’t that enough?
How much more needs to happen before you believe me, Mom?
I love you, more than anything.
I want you more than anything... I’ll keep saying it,
and I’ll never stop meaning it. If it’s just the two of us,
You’re strong, \N[1]. You’ve grown so much recently...
I know you’ll be okay on your own, and with the money
you’re making you should be able to afford your place
without your father’s support very soon.
Heck, I bet you’ll have that place crawling
with girls trying to get in your pants now
that I’m not going to be around.
I’ve seen some of the glances you’ve been getting around
town, like that little flirt at the dress shop...
Heh, maybe... Even if that happened,
I don’t think anyone could replace you.
You’ll always be my Mom, my favorite girl..
Yes... To all of it. For as long as you’ll let me, Kiddo.
Jeez, you’re... Uh, you’re still hard, aren’t you?
Gosh, it’s so big... It goes all the way to your knee...
I wish there was more we could do...
Mmmm... Speaking of, what was... Uh, what were you going
to do back there... before Dad called?
Hm? Oh I... I’m not really sure, myself.
What... What did you think would happen..?
I mean, there was that ONE thing...
My mouth, you mean... With my mouth?
You want me to do that for you again?
Right, I uh... I want you to do whatever you
feel comfortable doing, but uh... Yeah.
I- I can pull over to that alley or-
There’s your father, he sees us.
Shoot, what are we going to do with you?
You can’t go anywhere like this!
H-Hold on - just-!... You get out first and distract him
over on your side. I’ll, um, I’ll try to hold it down and
hide it in these damn pants. I don’t know what else to do...
Dammit, I just had to... Why can’t I control myself?!
<Just going to have to have my hand in my fucking
pocket all night holding this thing down, I guess...>
Paul, where’s Ashley? Isn’t she coming?
Your smart-mouthed daughter decided that goblins-
and-whatever-the-hell was more important, she’s staying
the night over with one of her friends, that braces girl.
All that time shopping and this is what you decided on?
Don’t you think it comes off a bit... Promiscuous?
What’s wrong with it? I like it! Thought you would too...
Leslie, you’re falling out of that top! Didn’t they have
something, y’know, in your size? Or at least more modest?
This is a nice place, I don't even know if they'll
let you in looking like this. They're gonna think you're a-
Dammit, we just got here and already you’re starting!
This is supposed to be a nice night, Dad.
Can you not be a dick, for once? Mom searched for a long
time to find something she felt good in, it wouldn’t
kill you to compliment her every once in a while!
And just what in the Hell is this get-up you got on?
It’s a suit, just nicer than yours.
Our table’s been ready for a while now,
if we make them wait any longer they'll give it away.
Don’t listen to him, Mom. You look absolutely amazing in
that dress, and you're gonna be the sexiest woman this
place has ever had in it.
C’MON! We’re late as it is -
quit screwing around in the damn parking lot!
Here we are! Let’s put him in the back seat...
Nnnngh... I wanna sit... Up front...
He’s out, how are you doing?
I feel good, really good... Ready to get home...
You’ll drive the speed limit, Mister...
Being excited is no excuse for not being safe...
But let’s try to get home quick!
